<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Dashboard</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex;
            margin: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .sidebar {
            width: 15%;
            background-color: #1E3A5F;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            padding: 1.5rem;
        }

        .sidebar a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .sidebar a:hover {
            background-color: #3b5c87;
        }

        .sidebar .logout {
            margin-top: auto;
            background-color: #FF6666;
        }

        .content {
            flex: 1;
            padding: 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .welcome {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .stat-box {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .details {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .notifications {
            flex: 2;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .notification-item {
            background-color: #76B6F8;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .notification-item h3 {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .sidebar .logout {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding: 0.8rem 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 4px;
            background-color: #FF6666;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .calendar {
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .create-event {
            background-color: #1E3A5F;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .calendar-box {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            flex: 1;
        }

        .event {
            background-color: #76B6F8;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="sidebar">
    <a href="#">Dashboard</a>
    <a href="#">Meetings</a>
    <a href="#">Friends</a>
    <a href="#">Notification</a>
    <a href="#">Settings</a>
    <a href="#" class="logout">Logout</a>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <div class="welcome">Hello Mark! It's good to see you again.</div>

    <div class="stats">
        <div class="stat-box">
            <h2>11</h2>
            <p>Events this month</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
            <h2>2</h2>
            <p>Organizer</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-box">
            <h2>9</h2>
            <p>Guest</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="details">
        <div class="notifications">
            <div class="notification-item">
                <h3>Birthdays this month</h3>
                <p>Louise - 18.04.2024</p>
                <p>Brad - 30.04.2024</p>
            </div>
            <div class="notification-item">
                <h3>Other</h3>
                <p>Wedding anniversary - 22.04.2024</p>
            </div>
            <div class="notification-item">
                <h3>Keep in touch</h3>
                <p>Hey, it looks like you havenâ€™t caught up with [Name1], [Name2], and [Name3] in over a month!</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="calendar">
            <div class="create-event">Create Event</div>
            <div class="calendar-box">
                <h3>Today</h3>
                <p>Dinner with Anna</p>
                <p>Louise's birthday party</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>


